      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/billionaire-adani-s-new-copper-foray-to-further-tighten-world-s-ore-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼(Gautam Adani)在印度的铜厂计划明年开工，这将刺激精矿进口大幅增加，进一步收紧冶炼厂所依赖的全球矿石供应。]]></description>
